          "source_html": "<div class=\"group\">\n      <h4>Questions 14-20</h4>\n      <p>Reading Passage has eight sections, A-H.</p>\n      <p>Which section contains the following information?</p>\n      <p>Write the correct letter, A-H, in boxes 14-20 on your answer sheet.</p>\n      <p><strong>NB You may use any letter more than once.</strong></p>\n      \n      <a id=\"q1-anchor\"></a>\n      <div id=\"q1-section\" style=\"padding:8px 0;border-top:1px dashed var(--line);\">\n        <span class=\"question-number\">14.</span> a description of a barrier designed to stop dingoes, which also divides two kinds of non-native animals\n        <div class=\"heading-options\">\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"A\"> A</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"B\"> B</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"C\"> C</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"D\"> D</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"E\"> E</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"F\"> F</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"G\"> G</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"H\"> H</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <a id=\"q2-anchor\"></a>\n      <div id=\"q2-section\" style=\"padding:8px 0;border-top:1px dashed var(--line);\">\n        <span class=\"question-number\">15.</span> how dingoes ensure that rival species do not dominate\n        <div class=\"heading-options\">\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"A\"> A</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"B\"> B</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"C\"> C</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"D\"> D</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"E\"> E</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"F\"> F</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"G\"> G</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"H\"> H</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <a id=\"q3-anchor\"></a>\n      <div id=\"q3-section\" style=\"padding:8px 0;border-top:1px dashed var(--line);\">\n        <span class=\"question-number\">16.</span> a reference to a widespread non-native species that other animals feed on\n        <div class=\"heading-options\">\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"A\"> A</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"B\"> B</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"C\"> C</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"D\"> D</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"E\"> E</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"F\"> F</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"G\"> G</div>\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"H\"> H</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <a id=\"q4-anchor\"></a>\n      <div id=\"q4-section\" style=\"padding:8px 0;border-top:1px dashed var(--line);\">\n        <span class=\"question-number\">17.</span> a mention of the dingo's arrival in Australia\n        <div class=\"heading-options\">\n          <div class=\"heading-option\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\